== Projects using circuits ==

=== Applications written in circuits ===

* [[http://sahriswiki.org|SahrisWiki]]
  -- a Wiki / CMS / Blogging Engine.
* [[https://bitbucket.org/prologic/kdb|kdb]]
  -- a pluggable IRC Bot Framework.
* [[https://bitbucket.org/prologic/irclogger|irclogger]]
  -- An IRC Bot that logs IRC Channels.
* [[https://bitbucket.org/prologic/ircnotifier|ircnotifier]]
  -- An IRC Bot with an integrated Web API that listens for Bitbucket/Github Repository updates and posted them to an IRC Channel.
* [[http://ccav.terranova.org.au/|Climate Chnage and Adaptation Visualiation]]
  -- Climate Chnage and Adaptation Visualiation Tool for the [[https://terranova.org.au/|TerraNova]] Projec.t

=== Applications integrating circuits ===

* [[http://realxtend.org|realXtend]]
  -- Next generation virtual worlds viewer; Naali, for Python components.
  Worked on by Toni Alatalo and Petri Aura at
  [[http://www.playsign.net|Playsign]] in collaboration with other
  realXtend developers.
* [[http://www.pwc.com|PriceWaterHouseCoopers]]
  -- [[http://www.tams.com.au|TAMS]] Report Generator written by James Mills
  and Michael Anton.
* [[http://mangahelpers.com|Mangahelpers]]
  -- Profiler for checking our webpages generation times, SQL and cache queries
  times, project page on https://launchpad.net/website-profiler

=== Other Uses of circuits ===

* [[http://media.mit.edu|MIT Media Labs]]
  -- Uses circuits for several internal prototypes

== 3rd Party Components ==

Here is a list of 3rd-party components that add to the available library of
components for circuits.

* [[https://pypi.python.org/pypi/circuits-bricks/|circuits-bricks]]
  -- General purpose components extending the circuits framework.
* [[https://pypi.python.org/pypi/circuits-minpor/|circuits-minpor]]
  -- A minimal portal based on the circuits component library.
* [[https://pypi.python.org/pypi/cocy/|cocy]]
  -- A components library for UPnP.

----
If you would like to add to any of these lists, please
[[https://bitbucket.org/circuits/circuitsframework.com/fork|Fork] the website
and submit a [[https://bitbucket.org/circuits/circuitsframework.com/pull-request/new|Pull Request]].
